1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,130
Release me!

2
00:00:01,410 --> 00:00:02,410
You vile wretches!!

3
00:00:03,910 --> 00:00:05,880
How many times must I punish you

4
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:07,120
before you are chastened?!

5
00:00:13,190 --> 00:00:14,190
Father.

6
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:15,490
You vile abomination!

7
00:00:15,530 --> 00:00:17,100
How dare you disgrace me?

8
00:00:17,740 --> 00:00:19,480
And you! You foul wretch!

9
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:22,700
Do you realize
what you have committed?!

10
00:00:24,930 --> 00:00:26,200
Fetch him here!

11
00:00:31,150 --> 00:00:32,040
- No!
- Saen!
Saen!

12
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:33,700
Saen!

13
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,590
Harm him not, I beg you.

14
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:39,000
Begone, you ungrateful son!

15
00:00:42,550 --> 00:00:43,250
Father...

16
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:44,840
Call me not Father!

17
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:48,480
I love Saen.

18
00:00:49,800 --> 00:00:51,200
I love him truly.

19
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:54,000
Pray...

20
00:00:55,570 --> 00:00:56,990
Pray, do him no harm.

21
00:00:58,130 --> 00:01:01,080
If you wish to die for a lowly wretch,

22
00:01:01,220 --> 00:01:02,820
so be it!!

23
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:07,780
You are a man.

24
00:01:07,820 --> 00:01:09,230
He is a man.

25
00:01:09,270 --> 00:01:12,560
How long shall you continue
to bring shame upon me?!

26
00:01:14,180 --> 00:01:14,930
Father...

27
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:16,260
I am not your father!

28
00:01:16,620 --> 00:01:19,120
Unless I draw blood from his head,

29
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:20,730
call me not Father!!

30
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,780
Father!

31
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,740
Pray, no more!

32
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:28,240
Or must I see you perish as well?!

33
00:01:28,390 --> 00:01:29,320
Begone!

34
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:33,130
If punishment must be given,

35
00:01:34,130 --> 00:01:35,490
let it be I alone who bears it.

36
00:01:35,670 --> 00:01:36,600
My dear!

37
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:37,630
Saen!

38
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,810
My dear!

39
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:42,760
If you lay hands upon Rak,

40
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,800
you must take my life as well.

41
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,720
Do not interfere.

42
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,840
This is my matter.

43
00:01:51,340 --> 00:01:52,870
I am his father!

44
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:55,440
Am I not his mother, then?

45
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:57,050
This is your doing!

46
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,550
You have raised him ill!

47
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:04,880
Because you would not hear our sons,

48
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,270
I have let them do as they please.

49
00:02:07,890 --> 00:02:09,590
First it was Rit,

50
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:11,460
and now it is Rak.

51
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:15,580
We have already lost a son...

52
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:20,520
Is it not enough?!

53
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,480
What is it you mean?

54
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:30,960
It seems...

55
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:35,000
the bearer of this news

56
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,440
shall not be me.

57
00:03:02,130 --> 00:03:02,920
Prink?

58
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:07,580
What brings you back here?

59
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,720
She brings you the news.

60
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:18,910
What news?

61
00:03:24,010 --> 00:03:26,180
It concerns Rit, Your Excellency.

62
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,540
Rit?

63
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:30,260
What of him?

64
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,710
He is no more.

65
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,590
His fever has taken a turn for the worse.

66
00:03:44,170 --> 00:03:45,660
We had no money

67
00:03:46,690 --> 00:03:48,210
nor any physician.

68
00:03:50,230 --> 00:03:53,750
My herbal remedy brought him no relief.

69
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,030
And...

70
00:03:57,940 --> 00:04:00,540
He breathed his last but moments ago.

71
00:04:37,330 --> 00:04:38,330
Rit...

72
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:44,190
Your father is a man of means.

73
00:04:47,290 --> 00:04:49,470
Why did you not come to me?

74
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:51,890
You could have seen a physician,

75
00:04:55,230 --> 00:04:57,820
a Western physician at Siriraj.

76
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,270
I shall take you there.

77
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,210
Rit!

78
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,570
Rit...

79
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:25,140
Before he breathed his last,

80
00:05:26,710 --> 00:05:29,740
he entrusted me with a letter for Saen.

81
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,990
Saen,

82
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,930
if you receive this letter,

83
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:07,490
it means my days have come to an end.

84
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:10,100
Yet my spirit shall not rest

85
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,210
unless I am certain

86
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:15,520
that my wife and child shall be cared for.

87
00:06:16,050 --> 00:06:18,860
I pray you,
take care of Prink and my child.

88
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:22,650
Kan is a gentle child and seldom cries.

89
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:24,770
He cries only when he is hungry,

90
00:06:25,690 --> 00:06:27,570
yet his mother has not enough milk,

91
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,520
and so he must be fed with rice water

92
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,870
and coconut water instead.

93
00:06:33,350 --> 00:06:35,800
It is the only matter that troubles me,

94
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:38,190
that they may starve.

95
00:06:39,090 --> 00:06:40,450
If it be possible,

96
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:43,580
I ask you to take care of them.

97
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:46,310
I shall be most grateful.

98
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,710
I have none other upon whom to depend,

99
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,650
and so I must ask this of you,

100
00:06:52,110 --> 00:06:54,030
my only friend.

101
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:03,770
Kan is named after Thotsakan.

102
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,280
I hope that my child

103
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,650
may one day play the giant,
as his father once did.

104
00:07:42,910 --> 00:07:44,030
Rit!

105
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,430
Rit!!

106
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:58,400
There shall be no wedding today.

107
00:09:01,410 --> 00:09:02,880
It is not by my doing,

108
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,990
but because of the funeral.

109
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,580
After the funeral,

110
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,710
we shall hold the wedding.

111
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:18,900
I shall be wedded as you wish.

112
00:09:24,220 --> 00:09:25,640
Did not that man

113
00:09:26,330 --> 00:09:28,340
attempt to flee your wedding?

114
00:09:30,010 --> 00:09:32,240
And yet you would compel him to wed you.

115
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:36,550
I compel no one.

116
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,960
It is you, Father,

117
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:40,860
who compels me.

118
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,690
I desired to...

119
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,880
secure for you the best of matches.

120
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:53,970
A woman must marry, at any cost.

121
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:57,140
She must have a family and children.

122
00:09:57,310 --> 00:09:59,240
Such is the custom.

123
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,710
Should she remain unwed,

124
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,700
she shall be held in ill regard.

125
00:10:09,350 --> 00:10:11,020
She must be a good daughter,

126
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:13,580
a good wife,

127
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,310
and a good mother.

128
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:17,780
Is it so?

129
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,820
Is that not the custom?

130
00:10:21,210 --> 00:10:23,700
What else could a woman be?

131
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:28,040
I wish to dance.

132
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:31,060
I wish to be a Khon dancer.

133
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:34,780
I wish to bring shame upon no one.

134
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,900
I only wish to do what I do best.

135
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:45,000
Khon is a tradition reserved for men.

136
00:10:45,930 --> 00:10:47,300
It is a royal performance

137
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,450
from which women are not permitted.

138
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,370
How could you dance among them?

139
00:10:53,610 --> 00:10:54,900
Now you see,

140
00:10:55,590 --> 00:10:56,990
whatsoever it is,

141
00:10:57,660 --> 00:10:59,460
there is no place for women.

142
00:11:02,810 --> 00:11:04,110
She cannot dance.

143
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,400
She cannot love.

144
00:11:07,890 --> 00:11:10,500
She is ever told no.

145
00:11:13,290 --> 00:11:14,810
I understand,

146
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,300
yet some matters

147
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:20,420
cannot change overnight.

148
00:11:22,090 --> 00:11:24,420
I ask you not to change the whole world.

149
00:11:25,830 --> 00:11:27,890
I only wish that you would understand

150
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,850
that women have hearts

151
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,320
and dreams.

152
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:38,140
Understand...

153
00:11:40,380 --> 00:11:42,220
how much suffering I endure.

154
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,760
Understand...

155
00:11:46,410 --> 00:11:47,920
how shameful it is

156
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:50,500
to pursue a man who loves me not.

157
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,500
Have I not a heart?

158
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:03,220
Tomorrow,

159
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:07,300
a nobleman of the inner court
is to study in England.

160
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:11,660
It is my wish...

161
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:15,340
that you accompany him
to study the performing arts.

162
00:12:18,740 --> 00:12:20,060
I can see that

163
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:22,860
you wish to perform.

164
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,470
Why not try it?

165
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:27,020
When you return,

166
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,620
you shall know yourself.

167
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:34,940
Will you truly let me go, Father?

168
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,380
If you wish to dance,

169
00:12:38,770 --> 00:12:41,420
you must dance with honor.

170
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,540
While you are there,

171
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:48,020
do not pursue a man
who knows not your worth.

172
00:12:49,730 --> 00:12:51,540
I shall bear it well in mind.

173
00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:44,700
The funeral is ended...

174
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:51,600
Our son is indeed gone.

175
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:01,240
You still have another son,

176
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:02,820
Rak,

177
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:07,260
and a young grandson.

178
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,180
What are we to do now?

179
00:15:17,610 --> 00:15:20,380
Leave, if such is your wish...

180
00:15:22,540 --> 00:15:24,570
I shall forbid none any longer.

181
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:32,380
I shall not leave.

182
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:35,700
Since Rit is gone,

183
00:15:37,490 --> 00:15:38,740
it is only I

184
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:43,740
who shall stay and care for
my father and mother.

185
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,620
If you stay with me,

186
00:15:49,730 --> 00:15:52,500
I shall never allow you to marry a man.

187
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,600
Father...

188
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:36,500
I beg your forgiveness

189
00:16:40,860 --> 00:16:42,610
for all past wrongs,

190
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,150
in word,

191
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,080
thought,

192
00:16:48,420 --> 00:16:49,550
and deed.

193
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:53,340
I never meant to bring shame upon you.

194
00:16:57,100 --> 00:16:58,160
I only wish to love

195
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:01,200
what my heart chooses,

196
00:17:06,650 --> 00:17:08,260
and I wish you to know it.

197
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:12,530
If I have caused you pain,

198
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:16,660
let it be my karma.

199
00:17:27,890 --> 00:17:29,180
I was wrong.

200
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,410
I am sorry

201
00:17:32,770 --> 00:17:36,500
for causing you suffering
and leaving you with no way out.

202
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:56,520
Your Excellency,

203
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:58,700
I beg your forgiveness

204
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:02,400
for all my past offenses.

205
00:18:04,090 --> 00:18:05,620
From this day onward,

206
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:08,360
Master Rak...

207
00:18:09,490 --> 00:18:10,380
and I...

208
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:13,720
shall remain as master and servant,

209
00:18:15,090 --> 00:18:16,400
and friends.

210
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:21,320
Pray allow me to serve in this manor

211
00:18:22,540 --> 00:18:24,380
and care for Master Rit's son,

212
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:27,040
as I am his foster father.

213
00:18:33,010 --> 00:18:35,660
If it be Rit's wish,

214
00:18:38,370 --> 00:18:39,820
so be it.

215
00:18:46,250 --> 00:18:47,220
I...

216
00:18:47,390 --> 00:18:48,790
shall be with Master Rak

217
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:51,380
as true friends.

218
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:55,650
We shall be side by side,

219
00:18:56,820 --> 00:18:58,500
though not together,

220
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:04,740
until the end of our days.

221
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:09,260
I thank you.

222
00:19:16,650 --> 00:19:17,820
From this day onward,

223
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:20,500
live as if

224
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,860
you were family.

225
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:27,840
I have brought Ms. Prink and little Kan
with me here.

226
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,270
Who are you calling "Ms."?

227
00:20:38,630 --> 00:20:40,830
Come here, my grandson.

228
00:20:41,370 --> 00:20:42,860
Come to your grandmother.

229
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:48,440
Come here, my grandson.

230
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:55,480
I am your grandmother,

231
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:59,640
and he is your grandfather.

232
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:05,040
Come, let me hold you.

233
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:11,120
Sit here upon my lap.

234
00:21:16,010 --> 00:21:18,560
He truly takes after Rit.

235
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:23,520
Prink,

236
00:21:24,650 --> 00:21:26,160
I thank you

237
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:29,160
for taking good care of his child.

238
00:21:33,330 --> 00:21:35,360
I am most grateful to you,
Your Excellency.

239
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:40,360
I shall continue to care for him

240
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:43,560
as long as my life allows.

241
00:21:49,790 --> 00:21:50,880
Prink,

242
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:53,520
come and sit here.

243
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:57,320
From this day onward,

244
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,760
you are of the family,

245
00:22:01,090 --> 00:22:03,240
as my daughter-in-law.

246
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:06,640
You shall live here from now on.

247
00:22:09,040 --> 00:22:10,540
Regard my wife

248
00:22:11,290 --> 00:22:12,680
and me

249
00:22:12,710 --> 00:22:15,080
as your other parents.

250
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:20,920
You may lie upon the bed
and sit upon the chair,

251
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:25,240
and be regarded as equal to my son, Rak.

252
00:24:03,970 --> 00:24:06,800
Tomorrow
I shall return to Phitsanulok, Saen.

253
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:09,060
I am filled with great shame.

254
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,470
Should I stay,

255
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,600
I shall feel my heart pierced.

256
00:24:25,010 --> 00:24:26,010
I understand

257
00:24:26,370 --> 00:24:28,060
that you take pride in yourself.

258
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:32,400
Do as you see fit.

259
00:24:35,580 --> 00:24:37,250
I shall return to farming

260
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:38,450
and tending the fields,

261
00:24:38,830 --> 00:24:39,830
to tend my mother,

262
00:24:40,560 --> 00:24:43,260
and to heal a fever in my heart,

263
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:46,160
a fever of love for you, Saen,

264
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:48,240
yet unrequited.

265
00:24:52,260 --> 00:24:54,120
In gratitude for what you did that night,

266
00:24:54,820 --> 00:24:56,260
I grant you leave to speak today.

267
00:24:58,730 --> 00:25:00,240
So unruly is his tongue

268
00:25:00,660 --> 00:25:02,240
that he has but few friends.

269
00:26:09,550 --> 00:26:12,770
Shortly thereafter, the King passed,

270
00:26:12,820 --> 00:26:15,880
and great changes came upon the land.

271
00:26:18,210 --> 00:26:20,000
Phranluang School was dissolved.

272
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:21,320
Royal performances were curtailed,

273
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:24,020
and government artists were reduced,

274
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:26,750
so as to preserve the kingdom's treasury.

275
00:26:26,780 --> 00:26:29,280
At last, the Department
of Royal Entertainments was dissolved.

276
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:33,190
From the golden age of artists

277
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:36,320
to an age in which puppets
were kicked about like rattan balls.

278
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:41,920
Yet Rak and Saen remained by their sides
in these trying times.

279
00:26:51,910 --> 00:26:52,900
Saen...

280
00:26:56,930 --> 00:26:58,960
Will you join me in opening
a private school for Khon?

281
00:27:04,230 --> 00:27:05,920
After the Department
of Royal Entertainments was dissolved,

282
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:09,720
Rak and Saen established
a private Khon school

283
00:27:10,650 --> 00:27:13,640
called the Saenrak Troupe.

284
00:27:16,230 --> 00:27:17,430
Meanwhile, little Kan,

285
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:19,560
the son of an artist,

286
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:21,540
- began learning Khon under Saen.
- Stand straight.

287
00:27:21,570 --> 00:27:23,400
Take the posture of an angry giant.

288
00:27:24,900 --> 00:27:27,520
Thotsakan must be firm in every step.

289
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:30,800
Lift your legs, bend your knees,

290
00:27:31,690 --> 00:27:32,920
and stamp your feet firmly.

291
00:27:33,350 --> 00:27:34,460
Once more.

292
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:36,040
The angry giant posture.

293
00:27:38,830 --> 00:27:40,560
Lift your legs, bend your knees.

294
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:44,560
Three, two, one.

295
00:27:48,230 --> 00:27:49,160
Very well.

296
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,740
Little Kan.

297
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:13,640
It is heavy, is it not?

298
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:15,560
Remember,

299
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,440
the Khon mask
should be held at your chest,

300
00:28:18,210 --> 00:28:19,360
not your neck.

301
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,160
Every posture
must bear the weight of the head.

302
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:27,240
It shall remain steady when you wear it.

303
00:29:23,930 --> 00:29:25,480
Do not overstrain yourself.

304
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:32,800
As much as my body can bear.

305
00:29:41,770 --> 00:29:43,040
Do not die for it.

306
00:29:49,050 --> 00:29:51,440
Should I die and be reborn
to dance Khon together once more,

307
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,980
no sorrow shall come of it.

308
00:29:59,700 --> 00:30:00,780
To this day,

309
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:03,740
you remain as graceful as ever.

310
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:09,960
Saen,

311
00:30:11,380 --> 00:30:13,000
you have such a sweet tongue.

312
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:16,520
It needs not be sweet.

313
00:30:17,550 --> 00:30:18,840
It only speaks the truth.

314
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,360
Saen...

315
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,990
Does this life

316
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,470
bring you sorrow?

317
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:05,900
We both

318
00:31:06,940 --> 00:31:08,460
may not end up together,

319
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:12,320
yet we shall remain side by side

320
00:31:14,120 --> 00:31:16,080
as long as Khon breathes.

321
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:20,280
Our Khon dance

322
00:31:21,090 --> 00:31:22,360
is like a wedding.

323
00:31:30,330 --> 00:31:31,800
All Khon students

324
00:31:33,220 --> 00:31:34,720
are as our offspring.

325
00:31:40,210 --> 00:31:41,680
Who else in this land

326
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:46,400
bears so many offspring as we do?

327
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:52,470
♫The moonflower blooms in dimming light,♫

328
00:31:52,530 --> 00:31:58,150
♫Its fragrance drifting through the night♫

329
00:31:58,180 --> 00:32:04,100
♫Though this love must brave the cold,♫

330
00:32:04,230 --> 00:32:08,260
♫We fear it not♫

331
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,200
We both

332
00:32:13,600 --> 00:32:15,180
may not end up together,

333
00:32:16,430 --> 00:32:18,200
yet we shall remain side by side

334
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:22,720
as long as Khon breathes.

335
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:32,930
♫Together evermore♫

336
00:32:59,700 --> 00:33:05,290
♫Yet night blooms perfume the dark,♫

337
00:33:05,390 --> 00:33:09,780
♫Long is the night♫

338
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:16,030
♫Bright is our love,♫

339
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:21,830
♫Behind the world's dark veil♫

340
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:29,690
♫I need not praise,♫

341
00:33:29,730 --> 00:33:34,540
♫Nor flowery flattery,♫

342
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:43,300
♫From any soul but you♫

343
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:49,640
♫Forevermore♫
